@EBookLibrary.WebApi_HostAddress = https://localhost:7096

### Register a new user
POST {{EBookLibrary.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

###

### Login and obtain JWT token
POST {{EBookLibrary.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@ebooklibrary.com",
  "password": "Admin1234!"
}

###

### List all genres (public)
GET {{EBookLibrary.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/genres
Accept: application/json

###

### List all books (public)
GET {{EBookLibrary.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/books
Accept: application/json

###

### Get a book by ID (replace with a real ID after seeding)
# GET {{EBookLibrary.WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/books/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
# Accept: application/json

###
